ze-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<span><font color="#000000" face="Calibri">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<strong style="font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold;"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">关于</span><font face="Calibri">VGOGO<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></font><span style="font-family: 宋体;">和芒果（旺旺</span><font face="Calibri">ID</font><span style="font-family: 宋体;">：芒果在飞）想说的几句话：</span></font></strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span><font face="Calibri">&nbsp; VGOGO</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">潮啸，从</span><span><font face="Calibri">12</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">月正式上线到现在，代码不断完善，已经更替</span><span><font face="Calibri">2</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个版本，目前开源的版本是功能最强大的版本。所有的程序都是跟着我的运营思路在走，所以现在要跟大家聊聊我的运营思路，如果思路相同，代码用起来也得心应手。</span></font></p>\r\n<p align="left" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: left;">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第一条：</span></b><span><font face="Calibri">U</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">站的定位非常重要，定位决定了</span><span><font face="Calibri">U</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">站的发展方向，有个方向叫什么都想做，那我跟你说，这是淘宝在干的事情，你等死吧！嘿嘿</span><font face="Calibri"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></font><span style="font-family: 宋体;">怎么在几千家</span><span><font face="Calibri">U</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">站找到自己的定位呢？这个我也不知道，我只有一句忠告：</span><font face="Calibri"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></font><b><span style="font-family: 宋体;">做最细分的市场，越有特色越好！</span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体;">定位完成的标志就是你确定了自己的类目</span><span><font face="Calibri">+</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">要定位的产品风格</span><span><font face="Calibri">+</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">有了自己想要的人群；（</span><span><font face="Calibri">PS</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">：</span><span><font face="Calibri">vgogo</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">虽然什么类目都做，可惜什么类目都没做透，而且人力成本非常高，编辑</span><span><font face="Calibri">2</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个，程序</span><span><font face="Calibri">1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个，美工</span><span><font face="Calibri">1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个，加芒果在飞，总共</span><span><font face="Calibri">5</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个人！常常还要从其他地方借调人员，最高的时候</span><span><font face="Calibri">8</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个人在更新内容，主要是要搞主图，搞专题，好累啊！）</span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000" face="宋体" size="3">&nbsp;</font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第二条：</span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体;">定位清晰就要有功能强大的后台来上产品，<b>一个功能强大的后台可以节省大量的人力成本。</b>原来我们家的产品也是手工一个一个输入，一天只能输入五十个产品，累死了，经过</span><span><font face="Calibri">2</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">个版本的改进，</span><span><font face="Calibri">Vgogo</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">后台，自带淘宝客录入商品，还能挑图片，实在是方便！</span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000" face="宋体" size="3">&nbsp;</font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第三条：</span></b><span><font face="Calibri">Vgogo</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的思路是</span><span><font face="Calibri">U</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">站能完成所有产品的展示，同时用户能非常方便的找到想要的商品，所以我们做了宝贝详情页，也做了各个类目的筛选，其实产品不多完全不需要那么多筛选。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<span><font color="#000000" face="Calibri">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span><font face="Calibri">VGOGO</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">的框架是根据网站需求决定的，首先我有下面几点的要求：</span></font></p>\r\n<ul style="margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; list-style: none; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc outside;">\r\n		<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">买家可以通过风格来找寻想要的商品（比如：甜美风格）；</span></font></li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc outside;">\r\n		<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">买家可以通过类目层层找到想要的商品（比如：衣服类目下的</span><span><font face="Calibri">T</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">恤）；</span></font></li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc outside;">\r\n		<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">买家可以通过某些特性找到想要的商品（比如：文艺范</span><font face="Calibri"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></font><span style="font-family: 宋体;">、</span><font face="Calibri"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></font><span style="font-family: 宋体;">森女等等）</span></font></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<span style="font-family: 宋体;"><font color="#000000">这就决定了一个产品有多个纬度。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span><font face="Calibri">VGOGO</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">这样来定义产品的纬度：</span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<img src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/17141840/T2G5fRXi0XXXXXXXXX_!!17141840.jpg" style="border: 0px; display: inline;" /><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong style="font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold;"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong style="font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold;"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">这些对应的后台功能又是那些？</span></font></strong></span></span></font></strong></p>\r\n<ul style="margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; list-style: none; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc outside;">\r\n		<strong style="font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold;"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">分类管理</span></font></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一件宝贝只能隶属一个分类，这样用户可以方便的通过这个分类找到对应的衣服；</span></font></p>\r\n<ul style="margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; list-style: none; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: disc outside;">\r\n		<strong style="font-style: inherit; font-weight: bold;"><font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">标签管理</span></font></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">每个标签都有自己的属性：比如说风格属性，比如材质属性，比如流行元素的标签；</span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">标签分为二种：</span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span><font face="Calibri">2.2.1<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">公共标签：公共标签是指所有的产品都需要的标签，比如风格或者品牌</span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span><font face="Calibri">2.2.2<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">类目标签：这个标签只属于这个类目</span><span><font face="Calibri">,</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">比如说</span><span><font face="Calibri">:<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">材质属性牛仔，这个只能在衣服类目里面，放鞋类就不合适了；</span></font></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding: 0px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一件宝贝可以同时拥有多个标签，如：图一所示，除了分类，其他都是标签</span></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>', '', '2013-04-16 22:01:59', 0, 0, 2),
